    "synopsis": "On the industrial world of Saltire Vex, Primaris Lieutenant Xedro Farren and his new-forged brothers are deployed alongside the Dark Angels and find their welcome cold. The t'au they face there are wounded and erratic, turning on their own as if driven by something they cannot name. As the campaign drags on, Farren comes to suspect that Interrogator-Chaplain Zaeroph's true quarry is not the xenos at all, but a psychic curse with the power to madden whole worlds. Pursuing the truth means pulling at threads the Unforgiven would rather leave knotted, and what Farren uncovers will test where his loyalty truly belongs.",
